Adoption Analytics Template

Schedule the Data Refresh for the Adoption Analytics App

The Adoption Analytics template creates a dataset called WaveChange, which collects logs that track how often users open CRM Analytics apps, dashboards, and lenses. Schedule the app to refresh daily.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available with CRM Analytics in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Access Adoption Analytics Templates and Apps and Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps.
Use CRM Analytics Templated Apps.

Set the app to refresh at least 1 hour after the WaveChange dataset is refreshed, usually overnight. Schedule your app refresh by following steps described in Schedule Data Refresh for a CRM Analytics App.
